JavaScript revision practice questions:
1.	Voting Eligibility System
You are tasked with building a system to check whether a person is eligible to vote. The system follows these rules:
•	A person must be at least 18 years old to vote
•	If the person is a citizen, they are eligible to vote
•	If the person is not a citizen but has passed a citizenship test, they are eligible to vote
•	If the person is below 18 no eligible
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        let age = parseInt(prompt("Enter Your Age: "));
        let citizen = prompt("Are You a Citizen? (yes/no)");
        let citizenship=prompt("Did you pass the citizenship Test? (yes/no)")
        if (age >= 18 && citizenship.toLowerCase() === "yes") {
            document.write("You Are Eligible To Vote");
        } else {
            document.write("You Are Not Eligible To Vote");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>


2.	Discount Eligibility
An online store offers a discount system based on the following condition:
•	A customer who spends more than Rs.100 gets a 20% discount.
•	A customer who spends a more than Rs.50 but less than or equal to Rs.100 gets a 10% discount
•	If the customer is a premium member they  receive an extra 5% discount.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        let amount=parseInt(prompt("Enter the amount: "))
        let premiumMember=prompt("Are you a premium menber?(yes/no)")
        if(amount>=100){
            a=amount*0.20
            document.write("Discount: "+a+"$")
        }
        else if(amount>50 && amount<100){
            a=amount*0.10
            document.write("Discount: "+a+"$")
        }
        else if(premiumMember==="yes"){
            c=amount*a*0.05
            document.write("Discount: "+c+"$")
        }
        else{
            document.write("No discount")
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>



